I'm in read-only mode — can only analyze, not edit. Here's the full diagnosis and the exact fixes needed:

---

### Issues found

**1. Three cramped columns** — `controls-row` has Prep / Synth / Effects all at `width: 1fr` side-by-side. On a typical terminal, each gets ~30 chars — effects get squished with their checkbox+param pairs.

**2. Bracket labels break rendering** — `[Load Source]`, `[ GENERATE ]`, `[ Play ]` etc. Textual `Button` expects plain text; the brackets look like broken ASCII art. Should be: `Load Source`, `Generate`, `Play`, `Browse`, `Clear DB`, `Stop`.

**3. Viz options (Colors/Chars) invisible** — they're inside `#gen-bar` at `height: 4`, which is only 4 terminal rows. The Output Path Input + Browse button already consume 3 rows, leaving 1 row for two Selects with labels — they get clipped.

**4. `ScrollableContainer` on controls** — user must scroll to see all effects. Should fit on one screen.

**5. Synthesis section overgrown** — 7 fields (Mode, Temp, Density, Segment, Crossfade, Seed) plus labels = 14 rows. Can merge into preprocessing or go below.

**6. `on_fx_change` still references old param Inputs** — after the removed sliders, the handler tries to `query_one(f"#fxp-...")` which will crash.

**7. Effects sliders were removed** — the patch accidentally deleted the per-effect parameter Inputs along with the `fx-row` Horizontal wrappers. Need to restore them.

---

### Required changes

**Button labels** (line 359-360, 416, 424, 427-428):
```
[Load Source]  →  Load Source
[Clear DB]     →  Clear DB
[...]          →  Browse
[ GENERATE ]   →  Generate
[ STOP ]       →  Stop
[ Play ]       →  Play
```

**Layout restructure** (lines 370-408) — replace 3-column `controls-row` with a 2-column layout, move synthesis inline:

```python
# MIDDLE: Controls
with Horizontal(id="controls-row"):
    # LEFT: Preprocessing + Synthesis
    with Vertical(id="prep-synth-col"):
        with Vertical(id="prep-section"):
            yield Label("PREPROCESSING", classes="section-title")
            yield Input(value="32000", id="sr", placeholder="Sample Rate (Hz)")
        with Vertical(id="synth-section"):
            yield Label("SYNTHESIS", classes="section-title")
            yield Select([("Fluid","fluid"),("Glitch","glitch"),("Evolving","evolving")], value="fluid", id="mode", prompt="Mode")
            with Horizontal():
                yield Input(value="0.5", id="temp", placeholder="Temp")
                yield Input(value="1.0", id="dens", placeholder="Density")
            with Horizontal():
                yield Input(value="1.0", id="seg", placeholder="Seg (s)")
                yield Input(value="0.1", id="xfade", placeholder="Xfade (s)")
            yield Input(value="42", id="seed", placeholder="Seed")

    # RIGHT: Effects (scrollable)
    with ScrollableContainer(id="fx-col"):
        with Vertical(id="fx-section"):
            yield Label("EFFECTS", classes="section-title")
            for fx_name, fx_info in EFFECT_REGISTRY.items():
                with Horizontal(classes="fx-row"):
                    yield Checkbox(fx_info["label"], id=f"fx-{fx_name}")
                    for pname, (pmin, pmax, pdef) in EFFECT_PARAMS.get(fx_name, {}).items():
                        yield Input(value=str(pdef), id=f"fxp-{fx_name}-{pname}",
                                    placeholder=pname, disabled=True)
            yield Static("", id="fx-status")
```

**CSS changes** (lines 785-812):
```css
#controls-box {        /* REMOVE — no longer needed */
    height: 1fr;
    border: solid $primary-background;
    padding: 0 1;
}
#controls-row {
    height: 1fr;       /* was: auto — fill remaining space */
}
#prep-synth-col {
    width: 1fr;        /* equal column */
    height: 1fr;
    border: solid $primary-background;
    padding: 0 1;
}
#fx-col {
    width: 1fr;        /* equal column */
    height: 1fr;
    border: solid $primary-background;
}
#gen-bar {
    height: 6;         /* was: 4 — need room for viz selects */
    border: solid $primary-background;
    padding: 0 1;
}
#viz-sel {
    height: auto;      /* ensure visible */
}
#gen-btns {
    width: 24;         /* was: 30 — tighter */
    height: 1fr;
}
```

**Fix `on_fx_change`** (line ~465) — restore param Input enable/disable:
```python
@on(Checkbox.Changed)
def on_fx_change(self, event: Checkbox.Changed):
    cid = event.checkbox.id or ""
    if cid.startswith("fx-"):
        name = cid.replace("fx-", "")
        self._enabled_effects[name] = event.value
        for pname in EFFECT_PARAMS.get(name, {}):
            try:
                inp = self.query_one(f"#fxp-{name}-{pname}", Input)
                inp.disabled = not event.value
            except Exception:
                pass
        self._update_fx_status()
```

---

Switch to a write-enabled mode and I'll apply all of these in one pass.

